data.description: Wellmaintained home, beautiful corner lot with fenced backyard and side entry garage. Entry opens to a formal diing room area, family room with beautiful stone fireplace, granite in the kitchen with eating bar and breakfast area. Split bedroom plan, garden tub and sep shower in the master. Great location, rural feel in a small neighborhood with easy excess to Covington and Conyers.
